704135f-a.title: Brooklyn: Emmons Avenue - Bragg Street
704135f-a.text:
Emmons Avenue, at the N. W. corner of Bragg Street, show-
ing several summer bungalows in the Sheepshead Bay area.
June 13, 1940
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS

704136f-a.text:
Emmons Avenue, at the N. E. corner of Bragg Street,

doorway reads:
Baptiste
Seagoing Cruisers

of Fine Cruisers
